Description: The Rest on the Flight into Egypt; landscape with the Holy Family seated under a tent at centre, a braying donkey in background at left; after Bernardino Passeri. c.1581 Engraving
Curator's comments: A copy from the engraving by Cort after Passeri. This is a worn impression.
